<topic id='element_date_time_of_birth__baby_.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Data Element: DATE TIME OF BIRTH (BABY) - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_date_time_of_birth__baby_">DATE TIME OF BIRTH (BABY)</xref>
 is the same as attribute 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_person_birth_date">PERSON BIRTH DATE</xref>
 and 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_person_birth_time">PERSON BIRTH TIME</xref>, from the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_end_date">End Date</xref>
 and 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_end_time">End Time</xref>
 of the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_fetus_episode">Fetus Episode</xref>.        </p>
      <p>The date corresponds to:</p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
the 
                                <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_person_birth_date">PERSON BIRTH DATE</xref>
 of the baby, where a 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_registrable_birth">REGISTRABLE BIRTH</xref>
 was recorded                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>or</p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
the recorded 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_end_date">End Date</xref>
 of the 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                        keyref="business_definition_fetus_episode">Fetus Episode</xref>, where the mother miscarried a Fetus (unborn baby) during the associated 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                        keyref="business_definition_maternity_episode">Maternity Episode</xref>
 i.e. where the pregnancy ends in or before the 24th week of gestation (which excludes it being recorded as a 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_registrable_birth">REGISTRABLE BIRTH</xref>).                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
  </div>
</body>
